{"115138":{"value":{"Media":{"id":115138,"idMal":41261,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/115138","status":"FINISHED","season":"SPRING","type":"ANIME","format":"OVA","seasonYear":2020,"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/115138-KDpOVgLKv36A.jpg","episodes":2,"synonyms":["Gishi wa Yanmama Junyuu-chuu","My Big Sister Is Breastfeeding","My Former-Delinquent Sister is Breastfeeding","형수는 양마마 수유중"],"isAdult":true,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":74,"description":"Based on the CG collections by Chinjao Girl. (チンジャオ娘。).\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\"What's wrong? Do you wanna suck my tits? lol\"\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nPlaced before scenes of his big sister's defenseless breastfeeding, this little brother finally gives way to his sexual drive...!\u003cbr\u003e\nWill he be able to impregnate her before her husband does!?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: DLsite English)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote: It has live-action AV adaptations: EYAN-181 (2022/05/17) and SONE-201 (2024/05/28).\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Hentai"],"duration":17,"title":{"native":"義姉はヤンママ授乳中","romaji":"Ane wa Yanmama Junyuu-chuu","userPreferred":"Ane wa Yanmama Junyuu-chuu"},"coverImage":{"color":"#e4935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx115138-oZHgSvWaOeSp.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx115138-oZHgSvWaOeSp.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx115138-oZHgSvWaOeSp.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":5,"month":6,"year":2020},"endDate":{"day":3,"month":7,"year":2020}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T06:25:53.583831+03:00"},"122954":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/122954-VWG2FUFnvzp2.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6865d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx122954-kOisr0EF5mRW.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx122954-kOisr0EF5mRW.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx122954-kOisr0EF5mRW.jpg"},"description":"Tasaki is caught peeking by a group of gals who use the evidence to blackmail him into becoming their slave. One day Tasaki manages to hypnotize his masters. And so his revenge begins.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: fourberie)","duration":17,"endDate":{"day":5,"month":3,"year":2021},"episodes":4,"format":"OVA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":122954,"idMal":43465,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":72,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2021,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/122954","startDate":{"day":5,"month":2,"year":2021},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["イジラレ ～復讐催眠～","Ijirare: Fukushuu Sai***","Bullied ~Revenge Hypnosis~","Izirare ~Hukusyu Saimin~"],"title":{"native":"イジラレ ～復讐催○～","romaji":"Ijirare: Fukushuu Saimin","userPreferred":"Ijirare: Fukushuu Saimin"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:01:56.496651+03:00"},"132203":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/132203-Vks73Lishg1I.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bba1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx132203-s7yzfJv6d48L.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx132203-s7yzfJv6d48L.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx132203-s7yzfJv6d48L.jpg"},"description":"Some gyarus have decided to use Imaizumi's house as a gathering spot to play video games and eat snacks. When Reina gets bored with video games, she sets her sights on another toy in the house: Imaizumi himself...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Fakku!)","duration":17,"endDate":{},"format":"OVA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":132203,"idMal":48755,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":77,"season":"SUMMER","seasonYear":2021,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/132203","startDate":{"day":6,"month":8,"year":2021},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Imaizumi Brings All The Gyarus To His House","Imaizumi's house is a place for gals to gather"],"title":{"english":"Imaizumi's house seems to be a gathering place for gals","native":"今泉ん家はどうやらギャルの溜まり場になってるらしい","romaji":"Imaizumin-chi wa Douyara Gal no Tamariba ni Natteru Rashii","userPreferred":"Imaizumin-chi wa Douyara Gal no Tamariba ni Natteru Rashii"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:01:56.021115+03:00"},"135584":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"KR","coverImage":{"color":"#e45043","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx135584-sFMfp8CDzleB.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx135584-sFMfp8CDzleB.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx135584-sFMfp8CDzleB.png"},"description":"After losing his parents at a young age, Mignon lives as a mechanic by day, and a cage fighter by night at an illegal arena. Living a life of exploitation and violence, the only person who gives him any attention is Oh Young-One, a doctor at the illegal arena.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003e“I’ll do anything…! I… I can help you!”\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDespite knowing Young-One’s true identity, Mignon’s pure and blind love for him causes Young-One to start slowly opening his heart. But the hellish reality that surrounds Mignon starts to shake up even Young-One’s life!","duration":5,"endDate":{"day":11,"month":8,"year":2023},"episodes":12,"format":"ONA","genres":["Drama","Romance","Sports","Supernatural"],"id":135584,"idMal":49430,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":78,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/135584","startDate":{"day":11,"month":8,"year":2023},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"native":"민용","romaji":"Mignon","userPreferred":"Mignon"},"trailer":{"id":"kcupE5zz3AY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kcupE5zz3AY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:01:56.2721+03:00"},"142116":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#35aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142116-9pjiwj1hc1Rm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142116-9pjiwj1hc1Rm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx142116-9pjiwj1hc1Rm.jpg"},"duration":30,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":2,"year":2022},"episodes":1,"format":"OVA","genres":["Hentai"],"id":142116,"idMal":50488,"isAdult":true,"meanScore":74,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2022,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/142116","startDate":{"day":25,"month":2,"year":2022},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Garden -The Two Flowers of the Takamine Family- THE ANIMATION","native":"Garden ～高嶺家の二輪花～ The Animation","romaji":"Garden: Takamine-ke no Nirinka The Animation","userPreferred":"Garden: Takamine-ke no Nirinka The Animation"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T23:01:56.270912+03:00"},"166613":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166613-drS86exJlIjG.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49328","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166613-uHB8q3D4qbon.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eJigokuraku\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166613,"idMal":55825,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1772981040,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":568841},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166613","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Hell’s Paradise: Jigokuraku Season 2","สุขาวดีอเวจี","Адский рай"],"title":{"english":"Hell’s Paradise Season 2","native":"地獄楽 第二期","romaji":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JLe_NUnAZVs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JLe_NUnAZVs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-02T03:43:20.520285+03:00"},"166617":{"value":{"Media":{"id":166617,"idMal":55830,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166617","status":"RELEASING","season":"WINTER","type":"ANIME","format":"TV","seasonYear":2026,"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166617-P4w3p0H4lE1O.jpg","episodes":13,"synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":83,"description":"In a Holy Grail War, Mages (Masters) and their Heroic Spirits (Servants) fight for the control of the Holy Grail—an omnipotent wish-granting device said to fulfill any desire. Years have passed since the end of the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan. Now, signs portend the emergence of a new Holy Grail in the western American city of Snowfield. Sure enough, Masters and Servants begin to gather... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nA missing Servant class...\u003cbr\u003e\nImpossible Servant summonings...\u003cbr\u003e\nA nation shrouded in secrecy...\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd a city created as a battleground.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the face of such irregularities, the Holy Grail War is twisted and driven into the depth of madness. Let the curtain rise on a masquerade of humans and heroes, made to dance upon the stage of a false Holy Grail. \u003ci\u003eThis is a Holy Grail War covered in lies.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, Aniplex USA, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eSpecial premiere of Episode 1 in its English Dub occurred in Los Angeles at the Fate 20th Anniversary Showcase event and as well through Crunchyroll’s YouTube Channel on November 23, 2024 before the Japanese television premiere.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eThe Japanese advanced premiere occurred during the \"Fate New Year's Eve TV Special 2024\" on December 31, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"duration":25,"trailer":{"id":"k1G8EvZg_BY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k1G8EvZg_BY/hqdefault.jpg"},"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake","native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"coverImage":{"color":"#1a1af1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png"},"startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":559838}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T05:59:22.226319+03:00"},"167152":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/167152-6QxZG8Dmf1EL.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1935d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx167152-u0cBZkqDowHP.jpg"},"description":"In a world where heroism is a punishment, Xylo Forbartz, a condemned goddess killer, battles endless hordes of monstrous abominations as part of Penal Hero Unit 9004. Death is no escape, only a cycle of resurrection and relentless combat. But when Xylo encounters a mysterious new goddess, their unlikely alliance sparks a rebellion that could shatter the chains of eternal punishment.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003cbr\u003e\n- The first episode aired with a runtime of ~58 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Initially scheduled to air in October, 2025 \u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":167152,"idMal":56009,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":80,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773322200,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":559230},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/167152","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ผู้กล้าโทษประหาร : บันทึกการรับโทษของหน่วยผู้กล้าต้องโทษ 9004","용사형에 처함"],"title":{"english":"Sentenced to Be a Hero","native":"勇者刑に処す　懲罰勇者9004隊刑務記録","romaji":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku","userPreferred":"Yuusha Kei ni Shosu: Choubatsu Yuusha 9004-tai Keimu Kiroku"},"trailer":{"id":"GcRs1JC7xeg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GcRs1JC7xeg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-06T05:09:30.459106+03:00"},"172463":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/172463-3J2o3qQZadFJ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5093d6","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx172463-LnXqHzt74SJL.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx172463-LnXqHzt74SJL.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx172463-LnXqHzt74SJL.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003eJujutsu Kaisen\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAfter the Shibuya Incident, a deadly jujutsu battle known as the Culling Game orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo erupts across ten colonies in Japan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nHaunted by guilt over the mass killings in Shibuya and wary of Sukuna’s interest in Fushiguro, Itadori chooses not to return to Jujutsu High. Instead, he teams up with Choso to exorcise the countless cursed spirits unleashed by Noritoshi Kamo.\nAmid this chaos, the Jujutsu Headquarters revokes Yuji Itadori’s suspended death sentence and appoints special-grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu as his executioner. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nNewly awakened modern sorcerers and resurrected ancient ones,  now fighting as players in the Culling Game, collide with conflicting motives, driving the world once more toward an age ruled by jujutsu.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: TOHO Animation)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama","Supernatural"],"id":172463,"idMal":57658,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773329160,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":495840},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/172463","startDate":{"day":9,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Jujutsu Kaisen 3rd Season","呪術廻戦 第3期","JJK3","มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร จรดลล้างบาง พาร์ต 1"],"title":{"english":"JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3: The Culling Game Part 1","native":"呪術廻戦 死滅回游 前編","romaji":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shimetsu Kaiyuu - Zenpen","userPreferred":"Jujutsu Kaisen: Shimetsu Kaiyuu - Zenpen"},"trailer":{"id":"ruX3rIj3--w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ruX3rIj3--w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:42:00.166996+03:00"},"176276":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/176276-ES97CHqKSrLg.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx176276-rtF8mYd2OWw2.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx176276-rtF8mYd2OWw2.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx176276-rtF8mYd2OWw2.png"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eMato Seihei no Slave.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":176276,"idMal":58505,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1772719200,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":586301},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/176276","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mabotai 2","魔都精兵のスレイブ 第２期","Mato Seihei no Slave 2nd Season","ทาสสุดแกร่งแห่งหน่วยป้องกันอสูร ซีซั่น 2"],"title":{"english":"Chained Soldier Season 2","native":"魔都精兵のスレイブ2","romaji":"Mato Seihei no Slave 2","userPreferred":"Mato Seihei no Slave 2"},"trailer":{"id":"IDgkCjcNxtU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IDgkCjcNxtU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-26T22:08:19.397709+03:00"},"182255":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182255-wyHvp6zJbWsO.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5dc9f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182255-butzrqd4I0aC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182255-butzrqd4I0aC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182255-butzrqd4I0aC.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eSousou no Frieren\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":27,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":10,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":182255,"idMal":59978,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":89,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773410400,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":248924},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182255","startDate":{"day":16,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Провожающая в последний путь Фрирен 2","장송의 프리렌 2기"],"title":{"english":"Frieren: Beyond Journey’s End Season 2","native":"葬送のフリーレン 第2期","romaji":"Sousou no Frieren 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Sousou no Frieren 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"RH-FcW94z00","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RH-FcW94z00/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-10T19:51:17.058038+03:00"},"182587":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/182587-SLNmuinewbUF.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45df1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx182587-fsU8LOjmd7oj.jpg"},"description":"The third season of \u003ci\u003e[Oshi no Ko]\u003c/i\u003e.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe story enters a new stage.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIt's been six months since \"POP IN 2\" was released. Thanks to MEM-Cho's hard work, B-Komachi is about to get their major break. Aqua is a multi-talented entertainer, and Akane's career as a talented actress is going smoothly. Meanwhile, Kana lost the cheerfulness she once had. To track down the truth behind Ai and Goro's deaths, Ruby keeps rising in the entertainment world...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eUsing lies as a weapon.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":11,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":182587,"idMal":60058,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":84,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1772632800,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":415577},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/182587","startDate":{"day":14,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["[OSHI NO KO] Season 3"],"title":{"english":"【OSHI NO KO】Season 3","native":"【推しの子】第3期","romaji":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season","userPreferred":"[Oshi no Ko] 3rd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JGYY6Pui5Kc","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JGYY6Pui5Kc/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-27T21:33:43.765151+03:00"},"184951":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/184951-Rx1mZZfKa9IU.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184951-s8Lg2muPBhdX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184951-s8Lg2muPBhdX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx184951-s8Lg2muPBhdX.jpg"},"description":"Suzuki’s a high school girl in love, but the guy she’s fallen for is nothing like her! While she’s cheerful, outgoing, and always trying to fit in, her classmate Yusuke Tani is stoic, quiet, and doesn’t seem to care what people think of him. Will Suzuki be able to overcome her anxieties and ask him out, or will she discover that opposites really don’t attract?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":184951,"idMal":60371,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1772956800,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":544601},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184951","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ลุ้นรักฉบับคู่ต่างขั้ว","정반대의 너와 나"],"title":{"english":"You and I Are Polar Opposites","native":"正反対な君と僕","romaji":"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku","userPreferred":"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku"},"trailer":{"id":"b5vpRUDkhT0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/b5vpRUDkhT0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-02T03:43:19.748745+03:00"},"187901":{"value":{"Media":{"id":187901,"idMal":61196,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187901","status":"RELEASING","season":"WINTER","type":"ANIME","format":"TV","seasonYear":2026,"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187901-03I5T8QVX1FG.jpg","episodes":12,"synonyms":["デドアカ","เดดแอ็กเคานต์ พิฆาตบัญชีมรณะ"],"isAdult":false,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","meanScore":62,"description":"Always ready for a fight! Destruction for destruction’s sake! The online streamer Aoringo is a troll, making the worst of the worst of boundary-pushing flamebait content and raking in the revenue from the hate-watchers. You may think he’s nothing more than a bottom feeder and a drain on society, but in reality, he’s high school dropout Souji Enishiro, a caring older brother with a sweet tooth who loves nothing more than his little sister. His viral videos? Just a way to pay his sister’s medical bills. And even if all of humanity hates him, he doesn’t care, so long as his little sister gets better. But then, something very strange begins to happen...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"duration":24,"trailer":{"id":"ynnk0CIyu10","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ynnk0CIyu10/hqdefault.jpg"},"title":{"english":"Dead Account","native":"デッドアカウント","romaji":"Dead Account","userPreferred":"Dead Account"},"coverImage":{"color":"#35bbf1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg"},"startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":559839}}},"updated_at":"2026-03-15T05:59:21.593268+03:00"},"187942":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187942-c2cZvunJGfiE.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187942-c2cZvunJGfiE.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187942-c2cZvunJGfiE.jpg"},"description":"When Arisu Yamabuki was all alone in bed at night, he was able to find solace in the voice of a radio host who went by “Apollo.” However, one day, she simply stopped broadcasting without any explanation. Years then passed, and Arisu is now a second-year high-schooler. He makes it his mission to search for Apollo, as there is something he wants to tell her. He doesn’t know what she looks like, or even what her real name is, but he manages to get some leads on her in his school’s broadcasting club. That’s where he meets four girls who all dream to get a job where they can make full use of their voices! Just who is Apollo, and how will those four’s dreams pan out?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: K Manga)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":187942,"idMal":61211,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773756000,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":595058},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187942","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mayochu","จูนเสียงใจไปสุดฝัน"],"title":{"english":"Tune In to the Midnight Heart","native":"真夜中ハートチューン","romaji":"Mayonaka Heart Tune","userPreferred":"Mayonaka Heart Tune"},"trailer":{"id":"poUibdNvxPQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/poUibdNvxPQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-10T19:42:22.371687+03:00"},"189565":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae78","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx189565-OHhadYSsd0Bg.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx189565-OHhadYSsd0Bg.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx189565-OHhadYSsd0Bg.jpg"},"description":"Eeyuu, a high school boy, has a problem! Two childhood friends \"Shio\" and \"Akari\" who go to the same high school are too cute! If they find out that I'm the only one looking sexually at them now that they've grown up, even though I have no intention of doing so... that would be too much! On the other hand, the two childhood friends also have their own secrets...? It's so awkward! It's complicated! But childhood friends are the best! A sweet and impatient love triangle love comedy where you can't be honest!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Kodansha, translated)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":24,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Romance"],"id":189565,"idMal":61359,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1773673200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":511724},"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/189565","startDate":{"day":6,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["OsaLove","幼ラブ"],"title":{"english":"You Can't Be In a Rom-Com with Your Childhood Friends!","native":"幼馴染とはラブコメにならない","romaji":"Osananajimi to wa Love Comedy ni Naranai","userPreferred":"Osananajimi to wa Love Comedy ni Naranai"},"trailer":{"id":"iSRJs8e5aRo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/iSRJs8e5aRo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-10T19:51:16.477315+03:00"},"192867":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/192867-r3UitttEQv8C.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1d6bb","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx192867-AXAu2LP7YA7Y.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx192867-AXAu2LP7YA7Y.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx192867-AXAu2LP7YA7Y.jpg"},"description":"Office Lady Tsuda Akane, age 28, seems like she’s got it all together. Beautiful, brainy, and an indispensable office worker for a robotics manufacturer, Akane’s admired at work…because her colleagues can’t see her at home. Privately, Akane’s a hot mess with an apartment that looks more like a landfill than a living space. Good thing she drunkenly ordered a new android named Nadeshiko to help her clean up! Well, maybe not good, because the beautiful lady android that arrives is a horny hottie. Akane’s about to get more service than she expected!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","duration":5,"endDate":{},"episodes":8,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Comedy","Ecchi","Romance","Sci-Fi"],"id":192867,"idMal":61694,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/192867","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Does it Count if You Lose Your Virginity to an Android?","はにすか","Hanisuka"],"title":{"english":"Does it Count if You Lose Your Innocence to an Android?","native":"アンドロイドは経験人数に入りますか？？","romaji":"Android wa Keiken Ninzuu ni Hairimasu ka??","userPreferred":"Android wa Keiken Ninzuu ni Hairimasu ka??"},"trailer":{"id":"SQAHZWo7x28","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SQAHZWo7x28/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-27T21:33:43.684413+03:00"},"207084":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/207084-QJoOYEulEDz5.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b207084-5ERIoIDjU76C.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b207084-5ERIoIDjU76C.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b207084-5ERIoIDjU76C.jpg"},"description":"In the distant future, on the outskirts left behind by the rapid concentration of advanced science and technology in urban areas, lies a remote mountain village known as Kagami Village.\u003cbr/\u003e\n“Behave yourself, or a Double will come for you.”\u003cbr/\u003e\nSuch old folklore still lingers in this village.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\nAkane Higure, a middle school student living in Kagami Village, has been eagerly awaiting the return of her older sister, Sui Higure, who is finally being discharged from the hospital after a year.\u003cbr/\u003e\nHowever, not long after her sister comes home, Akane receives a single phone call.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\n“The girl at home with you… isn’t your sister.”","duration":25,"endDate":{},"episodes":3,"format":"ONA","genres":["Mystery","Psychological","Supernatural","Thriller"],"id":207084,"idMal":63396,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2026,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/207084","startDate":{"day":31,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["OneGo","Playing Sister"],"title":{"english":"Playing Sister","native":"お姉ちゃんごっこ","romaji":"Onee-chan Gokko","userPreferred":"Onee-chan Gokko"},"trailer":{"id":"Asmti3OS0W0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Asmti3OS0W0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-07T00:36:08.666733+03:00"},"21":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21-wf37VakJmZqs.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e49335","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21-ELSYx3yMPcKM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21-ELSYx3yMPcKM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21-ELSYx3yMPcKM.jpg"},"description":"Gold Roger was known as the Pirate King, the strongest and most infamous being to have sailed the Grand Line. The capture and death of Roger by the World Government brought a change throughout the world. His last words before his death revealed the location of the greatest treasure in the world, One Piece. It was this revelation that brought about the Grand Age of Pirates, men who dreamed of finding One Piece (which promises an unlimited amount of riches and fame), and quite possibly the most coveted of titles for the person who found it, the title of the Pirate King.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nEnter Monkey D. Luffy, a 17-year-old boy that defies your standard definition of a pirate. Rather than the popular persona of a wicked, hardened, toothless pirate who ransacks villages for fun, Luffy’s reason for being a pirate is one of pure wonder; the thought of an exciting adventure and meeting new and intriguing people, along with finding One Piece, are his reasons of becoming a pirate. Following in the footsteps of his childhood hero, Luffy and his crew travel across the Grand Line, experiencing crazy adventures, unveiling dark mysteries and battling strong enemies, all in order to reach One Piece.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e*This includes following special episodes:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n- Chopperman to the Rescue! Protect the TV Station by the Shore! (Episode 336)\u003cbr\u003e\n- The Strongest Tag-Team! Luffy and Toriko's Hard Struggle! (Episode 492)\u003cbr\u003e\n- Team Formation! Save Chopper (Episode 542)\u003cbr\u003e\n- History's Strongest Collaboration vs. Glutton of the Sea (Episode 590)\u003cbr\u003e\n- 20th Anniversary! Special Romance Dawn (Episode 907)","duration":24,"endDate":{},"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy"],"id":21,"idMal":21,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":88,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1775398560,"episode":1156,"timeUntilAiring":2569252},"season":"FALL","seasonYear":1999,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21","startDate":{"day":20,"month":10,"year":1999},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ワンピース","海贼王","וואן פיס","ون بيس","วันพีซ","Vua Hải Tặc","All'arrembaggio!","Tutti all'arrembaggio!","Ντρέηκ, το Κυνήγι του Θησαυρού","OP","Ван-Пис"],"title":{"english":"ONE PIECE","native":"ONE PIECE","romaji":"ONE PIECE","userPreferred":"ONE PIECE"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-03-06T23:35:08.265511+03:00"},"21116":{"value":{"Media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21116-ZW9tJtFd7lWm.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e44386","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21116-wvQsXTMU3QDg.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx21116-wvQsXTMU3QDg.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx21116-wvQsXTMU3QDg.png"},"description":"After adorable “mermaid” Mamori is transferred to one of five artificial islands, she’s cornered, attacked and eventually saved by another beautiful transfer named Mirei. Unfortunately, even after the girl intervenes, Mamori’s attackers refuse to let up. Just when they think all hope is lost, Mirei and Mamori share a passionate kiss that turns the little “mermaid” into a powerful sword.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: FUNimation)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":26,"month":12,"year":2015},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Ecchi","Fantasy","Romance","Sci-Fi"],"id":21116,"idMal":30385,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":55,"season":"FALL","seasonYear":2015,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21116","startDate":{"day":10,"month":10,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid","native":"ヴァルキリードライヴ マーメイド","romaji":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid","userPreferred":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-27T21:34:00.427699+03:00"},"21413":{"value":{"Media":{"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21413-fPvW8uD5XIfM.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/21413-fPvW8uD5XIfM.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/21413-fPvW8uD5XIfM.jpg"},"description":"A series of specials included in the 'Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid' DVD/BD volumes.","duration":2,"endDate":{"day":25,"month":5,"year":2016},"episodes":6,"format":"SPECIAL","genres":["Action","Ecchi","Fantasy"],"id":21413,"idMal":31736,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"season":"WINTER","seasonYear":2016,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/21413","startDate":{"day":18,"month":12,"year":2015},"status":"FINISHED","title":{"english":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid Specials","native":"ヴァルキリードライヴ マーメイド ミニOVA","romaji":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid Mini OVA","userPreferred":"Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid Mini OVA"},"type":"ANIME"}},"updated_at":"2026-02-27T21:35:04.622651+03:00"}}
